  <h1>Refund & Cancellation</h1>
  <p>Effective Date: May 10, 2026</p>
</header>

<div class="content-wrap">
  <p>At Sugar Down, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. Since we provide health products, we follow a strict policy to ensure safety and hygiene while being fair to our customers.</p>

  <h2>1. Order Cancellation</h2>
  <p>You can cancel your order within <strong>2 hours</strong> of placing it. To cancel, please WhatsApp us at +91 8650777799 or call us immediately. Once the order is dispatched (usually within 24 hours), it cannot be cancelled.</p>

  <h2>2. Returns & Replacements</h2>
  <p>Due to the nature of Ayurvedic products, we only accept returns or provide replacements in the following cases:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The product received is damaged or leaked during transit.</li>
    <li>The product received is expired.</li>
    <li>The wrong product was delivered to you.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To request a replacement, please contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of delivery. You must provide a photo or unboxing video of the damaged/wrong product via WhatsApp.</p>

  <h2>3. Refund Policy</h2>
  <p>Refunds are processed only if a replacement is not possible for a valid return. Once approved, the refund will be credited to your original payment method within 7-10 working days.</p>

  <h2>4. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
  <p>Items that have been opened, used, or have broken seals are not eligible for return or refund due to health and safety reasons.</p>

  <h2>5. How to Initiate a Return</h2>
  <p>Please WhatsApp us at +91 8650777799 with your Order ID and the reason for return. Our team will guide you through the process.</p>

  <h2>6. Shipping Costs for Returns</h2>
  <p>If the return is due to a mistake on our part (damaged/wrong item), we will bear the shipping costs for the return and replacement.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact for Support</h2>
  <p>LUCKY HEART Support Team<br>
  Email: luckyheartayurveda@gmail.com<br>
  Phone: +91 8650777799<br>
  Address: Ward-9, Brahaman Wali Garli, Karnawal, Meerut, UP - 250344</p>
